metadata.description: Travel Toucans is a collection of 10,001 unique NFTs, each of which is a digital collectible living on the Ethereum blockchain. Your Travel Toucan serves as your membership to the first NFT lifestyle community centered on real-world travel! At TT, members share experiences, advice, and insider info about once-in-a-lifetime adventures. Learn more at [TravelToucans.club](https://traveltoucans.club/), and join the excursion!
metadata.name: Travel Toucan #1
